      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Tools return structured facts or structured errors.\nNo in-domain exceptions for:\nmisses, empty results, mode gates,\nor missing index data.\nThe model cites returned facts.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.05
